## Specified Customer [/api/customer/{?customer_id,customer_name,id_number}]

Provide a list of customer that fit with the given criteria.

+ Parameters
    + customer_id (string) - id of the customer
    + customer_name (string) - name of the customer
    + id_number (number) - national id of the customer

### List Customer with Conditions [GET]
+ Response 200

        [
            {
                "customer_id": "abc125",
                "customer_name": "Nguyễn Văn C",
                "gender": "1",
                "date_of_birth": "10/15/1980",
                "identifier": "263216352"
            }
        ]

