                "to": "Hanoi",
                "date": "10/22/2016",
                "time": "9:00:00",
                "price": "1000000"
            }
        ]

## Seats [/api/seat/{?free,flight_id}]

List current seat (and also their state) in flight with flight_id.

+ Parameters
    + free (boolean) - state of seats
    + flight_id (string) - id of flight

### List Seats [GET]
