## Seat Booking [/api/seat]

For booking seats. The POST method also create and return an unique Booking Identify Code.

### Book Seats [POST]

+ Request

        [
            "flight_id": "abcdef"
            [
                {
                    "seat_id": "ab15"
                },
                {
                    "seat_id": "ab16"
                }
            ],
            "customer_id": "abc123"
        ]

+ Response 201

        {
            "reservation_code": "abczzz"
        }

+ Request

        [
            "flight_id": "abcdef" 
            [
                {
                    "seat_id": "ab10",
                }
            ]
        ]
+ Response 400

